issue.title: Make prediction layout page
issue.body:
- Prediction layout page that should be popped up from an intent from the main layout 

Should have:
- An ImageView for the image loaded in
- Save button to save the image, maybe some may to embedded the prediction in there aswell? 
- Redo prediction button, which just recall the python code to predict again (not sure if this would actually be useful tbh but why not)
- A back button on the toolbar to return to main layout

issue.title: Python Interop/Using TensorFlowLite
issue.body:
Test to see if we can interact with python code from Java and how to use the output from a tensorflow model to make predictions on an image

I think this framework is our best bet: https://chaquo.com/chaquopy/
